text.header1: Vhura zvinongedzo Zvakachengeteka uye Zvisingazivikanwe uchishandisa Kasm Open-in-Isolation.
text.header2: Iyo Kasm Vhura muIsolation browser yekuwedzera inopa yekudzvanya-kurudyi menyu sarudzo yekuvhura webhu zvinongedzo muWebhusaiti yakasarudzika browser. Izvi zvinoita kuti zvive nyore uye zvisina musono kuvhura zvakachengeteka maURL anofungidzirwa/asina kuchengeteka kana kuchengetedza zvakavanzika zvako. Sezvo peji rewebhu richipihwa mukati meyekure workspace browser, pane kuurayiwa pakombuta yako yemuno, unokwanisa kupindirana zvakachengeteka uye usingazivikanwe newebhu peji.
text.header3: Ona zvinyorwa zveKasm kuti uwane rumwe ruzivo.

title.tooltip1: Enda ichavhura iyo URL munzvimbo itsva yekushanda, iyo Cast Kiyi nzira ndeye iripo inomhanya nzvimbo yekushandira
title.tooltip2: Kana uchivhura mameseji muKasm Workspaces sesheni kunze kwekunge tambo iri URL inoshanda inopfuudzwa kune yekutsvaga injini.
title.tooltip3: Kana uchivhura mameseji muPabasa rekushanda ungangoda kutsiva tambo dzakapfuudzwa kuWorkspace (Tsvaga inotsigira yakajairwa RegExp ine delimiters /regexp/g)
